    passion for dance.
  </p>
  <p>
    Shawn began teaching Lindy Hop in 2002 and co-founded New School Swing in Boston with Amanda
    Gruhl and Nicole Zuckerman, running it from 2010–2013 until he left for NYC. His journey into
    blues dancing began in 2006, teaching alongside Amanda Gruhl, and he soon became a force on
