    His blues and swing band, The Fried Bananas (co-led by Josh Fialkoff), played at major events
    across the country, leaving a lasting impact on the scene.
  </p>
  <p>
    After moving to NYC in 2014 he began studying Balboa with Mickey Fortanesce and went on to be
    mentored by Yurina Shin and Jen Barnett. Enthralled by the intricacies and deep communication
    skills of Balboa, he worked hard and started competing and placing in competitions, including
    1st in the 2026 Open Cal Bal Mix &amp; Match with Hannah Manning, 1st in the 2017 All Balboa
    Weekend Amateur competition, 1st in a Bal Love Strictly with Theresa Manney, 1st in a Snowball
    Mix &amp; Match with Amy Lu, 1st place in the Slow Balboa comp at Bal Week 2025 with Jen
    Barnett, 1st in a slow dance competition at Snowball, and more.
  </p>
  <p>
    Recently, Shawn's teaching has evolved to reflect his dedication to mindfulness and
    meditation, cultivating presence and flow. He brings not only technical expertise but also a
